            <title>[LU-6879] tgt_request_handle has unnecessary req-&gt;export != NULL check</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6879</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Added by recent multislot code:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;        tsi-&amp;gt;tsi_tgt = tgt = class_exp2tgt(req-&amp;gt;rq_export);
...
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;/* check request&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;s xid is consistent with export&apos;&lt;/span&gt;s last_xid */&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (req-&amp;gt;rq_export != NULL) {
...
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At this point we certainly cannot have NULL req-&amp;gt;rq_export so that condition is totally unneeded.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
